"9:93:19" : {s: 9, a: 93, w: 19, r: "علم", t: "يَعْلَمُونَ", l: "عَلِمَ", lc: 382, tl: "yaʿlamūna", lb: "(সে) জানে",e: "know", b: "তারা জানে", i: "mereka mengetahui", f: 81, rm: "to mark/sign/distinguish, creations/beings, world, science/learning/knowledge/information, aware/know. By means of which one knows a thing, hence it signifies world or creation, because by it the Creator is known. alim (pl. ulama) - one who is learned/wise or knows."},
